  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_34a18528-cb48-4203-9958-ab1641267d9c" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Course Navigation, click the <strong>Discussions</strong> link.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="duplicate-discussion" data-step-uuid="e459ad24-bd00-4163-b459-8e5b30858b3f">
    <h2 id="duplicate-discussion" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Duplicate Discussion</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <a href="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/144/340/original/3936501c-4f1e-4fd8-9a40-eb277563f92b.png" class="screensteps-image-zoom" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener noreferrer">
        <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/144/340/medium/3936501c-4f1e-4fd8-9a40-eb277563f92b.png" srcset="" alt="Duplicate Discussion" height="391" width="855">
      </a>
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_03e96147-2f8d-48c9-bb78-dff3b50c4053" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Locate the discussion you want to duplicate and click the <strong>Options</strong> icon [1]. Click the <strong>Duplicate</strong> link [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

